crack his knuckles.

563
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:54,081
Pop, pop, pop.

564
00:36:54,212 --> 00:36:55,082
Just like I said.

565
00:36:56,344 --> 00:36:57,084
Yeah, I hear it.

566
