wasn't the main target.

600
00:38:25,041 --> 00:38:25,303
Huh.

601
00:38:38,141 --> 00:38:39,012
Good boy.

602
00:38:41,231 --> 00:38:41,841
How's your head?

603
00:38:42,363 --> 00:38:43,103
It hurts.

604
00:38:43,495 --> 00:38:44,104
I bet.

605
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:46,193
Um.

606
