742
00:46:42,974 --> 00:46:43,583
Absolutely.

743
00:46:44,627 --> 00:46:45,498
Dinner?

744
00:46:45,628 --> 00:46:47,326
Done.

745
00:46:47,717 --> 00:46:50,503
Hey, Igor, search the
definition of acidic.

746
00:46:54,986 --> 00:46:55,813
