807
00:49:20,827 --> 00:49:21,610
Black with a black tie.

808
00:49:23,961 --> 00:49:25,005
Yeah.

809
00:49:25,266 --> 00:49:26,354
Can I get you a drink?

810
00:49:26,789 --> 00:49:28,182
No, I'm technically on duty.

811
00:49:28,313 --> 00:49:29,314
